com.mobius.vdrapi
Class VersionFieldType

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.mobius.vdrapi.VersionFieldType
public final class VersionFieldType
extends Object

Enumerates the different fields of a Version ID, and is used for parsing Version IDs so they can be reformatted. Use the GetBegin and GetEnd functions on a Version ID string to retrieve the String.substring(int) of the Version ID corresponding to the field.

See Also:
VersionIdFormatter, String.substring(int)
